def plane_seat(a):
    if a > 60 or (a < 1 and a % 10 > 0) or (a < 21 and a % 10 > 3) or (a >= 40 and a % 10 > 6):
        return 'No Seat!!'
    section = 'Front' if a <= 20 else 'Middle' if a <= 40 else 'Back'
    left_cluster = a % 10 <= 3
    letter = chr(ord('A') + a % 10 - 1)
    return f'{section}-{("Left" if left_cluster else "Right")}'
